    Note: identifier may begin a reference type whose full spelling can be a dotted
    Note: qualified name (java.util.List), a generic application
    Note: (Function<Integer,Integer>, Map<String,List<Integer>>), an array type
    Note: (String[]), or any combination - none of which a one-token peek can see.
