Grammar: 'new' (
  Type '(' ArgumentList ')' [ClassBody]                        object creation
  | Type ('[' Expression ']')+ ('[' ']')* [ArrayInitializer]    sized array
  | Type ('[' ']')+ ArrayInitializer                            initialized array
). The base type is parsed without trailing brackets so the '[' vs '('
following it selects array creation vs object (or anonymous-class) creation.
Array creation yields an AST_ARRAY_CREATION node whose first child is the
element type, followed by each dimension-size expression (an empty-bracket
