@Reasoning:
Public entry point. Delegates to parse_compilation_unit and returns the
root AST node. Single-call API hides the internal naming of the start
symbol.
@End Reasoning
Process called "parse" takes parser as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Parse complete Java source file

    Return proc parse_compilation_unit with parser
End Process

Note: End of Java Parser
